------------
v1.0.0alpha1
------------

First alpha release for Horde 4.
Forked from PEAR-Net_LDAP2-2.0.7.
Converted to PHP5 strict standards.
Converted to use exceptions.
Included functions from the previous Horde_LDAP for backwards compatibility.
